thread.title: Kathryn Pitt
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Kathryn Pitt

author: Kathryn Pitt
title: Kathryn Pitt
text: Staff is great. Took alittle to long to do the rental, but not bad. At arrival there where some very loud, angry and rude customers there, the staff did their best to handle the situation and get them done and out, while reminding them that my 4 year old was there too. That ment alot to me.
